Interface ReadonlyTable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    InnerTable, Serializable, Table
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AggregationFieldsTable, AllTableOptionsTable, AuditLogTable, BranchesTable, BucketsTable, CatalogOptionsTable, ConsumersTable, FileMonitorTable, FilesTable, ManifestsTable, OptionsTable, PartitionsTable, ReadOptimizedTable, SchemasTable, SinkTableLineageTable, SnapshotsTable, SourceTableLineageTable, StatisticTable, TableLineageTable, TagsTable

    public interface ReadonlyTable
extends InnerTable
    Readonly table which only provide implementation for scan and read.
